import React from 'react'
import { ChakraProvider, Box, Stack, Text} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Tweet = () => {
    const tweetBorderFirst = {
        borderTop: "1px solid #38444D",
        borderBottom: "1px solid #38444D",
      };

    const tweetBorder = {
    borderBottom: "1px solid #38444D",
    };

    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Box w="600px" minH="110px" style={tweetBorderFirst} ml="-17px" p="4">
                <Stack direction="row">
                    <Box>
                        <Box w="50px" h="50px" bg="gray.50" mt="10px" borderRadius="100%"></Box>
                    </Box>
                    <Box  minH="90px">
                        <Stack direction="column" mt="10px">
                            <Box>
                                <Stack direction="row">
                                    <Box>
                                        <Text fontSize="15px" fontWeight="bold" color="white">Chelsea FC Indonesia</Text>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Text fontSize="15px" color="#8899A6">@chelseafc_indo</Text>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Text fontSize="15px" color="#8899A6">15m</Text>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Box w="20px" h="10px" bg="gray.50" ml="178px"></Box>
                                    </Box>
                                </Stack>
                            </Box>
                            <Box>
                                <Text fontSize="15px" color="white">Menjelang akhir tahun 2020, simak momen-momen terbaik dari para rekrutan baru the Blues khususnya untuk tahun ini.</Text>
                            </Box>
                            <Box>
                                <Stack direction="row" spacing="70px">
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                </Stack>
                            </Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Box>

            <Box w="600px" minH="110px" style={tweetBorder} ml="-17px" p="4">
                <Stack direction="row">
                    <Box>
                        <Box w="50px" h="50px" bg="gray.50" mt="10px" borderRadius="100%"></Box>
                    </Box>
                    <Box  minH="90px">
                        <Stack direction="column" mt="10px">
                            <Box>
                                <Stack direction="row">
                                    <Box>
                                        <Text fontSize="15px" fontWeight="bold" color="white">Chelsea FC Indonesia</Text>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Text fontSize="15px" color="#8899A6">@chelseafc_indo</Text>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Text fontSize="15px" color="#8899A6">15m</Text>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Box w="20px" h="10px" bg="gray.50" ml="178px"></Box>
                                    </Box>
                                </Stack>
                            </Box>
                            <Box>
                                <Text fontSize="15px" color="white">Menjelang akhir tahun 2020, simak momen-momen terbaik dari para rekrutan baru the Blues khususnya untuk tahun ini.</Text>
                            </Box>
                            <Box>
                                <Stack direction="row" spacing="70px">
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Stack direction="row" spacing="15px">
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                            <Box w="20px" h="20px" bg="green.400"></Box>
                                        </Stack>
                                    </Box>
                                </Stack>
                            </Box>
                        </Stack>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
            </Box>
            

        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default Tweet
